Package Game

Class Game

  • java.lang.Object
    • Game.Game
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BasicGameSpiritFactory

    public class Game
extends java.lang.Object
implements BasicGameSpiritFactory
    Game object is a set of many GameObjects. it contains a Map for converting from geodetic coordinates to XY pixel coordinates on screen. it's also a BasicGameSpiritFactory allowing it to convert GameObjects into GameSpirit for visual representation.
